<li><cite class="citation journal">Gordon, Stewart (July–August 2009). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.saudiaramcoworld.com/issue/200904/the.game.of.kings.htm">"The Game of Kings"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Saudi_Aramco_World" title="Saudi Aramco World">Saudi Aramco World</a></i>. Houston: Aramco Services Company. <b>60</b> (4): 18–23.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Saudi+Aramco+World&amp;rft.atitle=The+Game+of+Kings&amp;rft.volume=60&amp;rft.issue=4&amp;rft.pages=18-23&amp;rft.date=2009-07%2F2009-08&amp;rft.aulast=Gordon&amp;rft.aufirst=Stewart&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.saudiaramcoworld.com%2Fissue%2F200904%2Fthe.game.of.kings.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+of+chess" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span> (<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20121003051322/http://www.saudiaramcoworld.com/pdf/2000/200904.pdf">PDF version</a>)</li>
<li><cite class="citation journal">Riddler, Ian; Denison, Simon (February 1998). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.britarch.ac.uk/ba/ba31/ba31feat.html">"When there is no end to a good game"</a>. <i>British Archaeology</i>. United Kingdom: Council for British Archaeology (31). <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Serial_Number" title="International Standard Serial Number">ISSN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.worldcat.org/issn/1357-4442">1357-4442</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=British+Archaeology&amp;rft.atitle=When+there+is+no+end+to+a+good+game&amp;rft.issue=31&amp;rft.date=1998-02&amp;rft.issn=1357-4442&amp;rft.aulast=Riddler&amp;rft.aufirst=Ian&amp;rft.au=Denison%2C+Simon&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.britarch.ac.uk%2Fba%2Fba31%2Fba31feat.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+of+chess" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li><cite class="citation journal">Wilkinson, Charles K (May 1943). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.goddesschess.com/chessays/chessmenandchess.html">"Chessmen and Chess"</a>. <i>The Metropolitan Museum of Art Bulletin</i>. The Metropolitan Museum of Art. New Series 1 (9): 271–279. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.2307%2F3257111">10.2307/3257111</a>. <a href="/wiki/JSTOR" title="JSTOR">JSTOR</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//www.jstor.org/stable/3257111">3257111</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Metropolitan+Museum+of+Art+Bulletin&amp;rft.atitle=Chessmen+and+Chess&amp;rft.volume=New+Series+1&amp;rft.issue=9&amp;rft.pages=271-279&amp;rft.date=1943-05&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.2307%2F3257111&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F3257111&amp;rft.aulast=Wilkinson&amp;rft.aufirst=Charles+K&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.goddesschess.com%2Fchessays%2Fchessmenandchess.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHistory+of+chess" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
